# Express Backend

Express 5, TypeScript, Prisma, auto-entity CRUD, security middleware, structured errors, request IDs, health checks, Docker, and Vitest.

```bash
cp .env.example .env
<%= pm.install %>
<%= pm.prismaExec %> generate
<%= pm.run %> dev
```

API health is available at `GET /api/health`.
Entity metadata is available at `GET /api/v1/_meta`.
